# Observable weights for LHC hadronization comparison study (pp at 7 TeV)
# Format: /regex/path/to/histogram   weight
#
# ATLAS event shapes in leptonic Z-events -- direct analogue of LEP event shapes
# Measures thrust, C-parameter, jet broadening in Z->ll events at 7 TeV.
# These are sensitive to the same string fragmentation parameters as LEP,
# but with additional pp context (ISR, UE, colour reconnection, etc.).
/ATLAS_2016_I1424838  1.0
